These are Puzzles for 2x3 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-1::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: juice, lemonade, soy-milk
3 different games are played: chess, monopoly, scrabble
1. the person playing monopoly is the person drinking lemonade##1
2. the person drinking soy-milk is between the person playing scrabble and the person drinking lemonade##2
3. the person drinking juice is on the right of the person playing chess##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |   3   |
| Beverage      | lemonade | soy-milk | juice |
| Game   | monopoly     | chess    | scrabble   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-2::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: drawing, rock-climbing, sudoku
City: liverpool, berlin, rome
1. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the left of the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
2. the person traveling to rome is between the person traveling to liverpool and the person who's hobby is drawing##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |       2       |       3       |
| Hobby   | drawing    | sudoku        | rock-climbing |
| City     | berlin | rome | liverpool         |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-3::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: cola, mirinda, tea
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: animation, fantasy, thriller
1. the person watching animation movies is on the right of the person drinking cola##1
2. the person drinking cola is between the person watching fantasy movies and the person drinking tea##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |    2     |  3  |
| Beverage   | mirinda | cola     | tea |
| Movie-Genre        | fantasy  | thriller | animation |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-4::.
There are 3 different favourite colors: lavender, ivory, blood-red
3 different pets are kept: bird, fish, goldfish
1. the person who likes lavender is the owner of the bird##1
2. the person who likes blood-red is between the owner of the fish and the owner of the bird##2
3. the owner of the goldfish is on the left of the owner of the bird##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |    2     |  3   |
| Color   | ivory  | blood-red     | lavender |
| Pet           | fish | goldfish | bird |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-5::.
There 3 different types of food: kiwi, apricot, papaya
3 different pets are kept: chinchilla, fish, goat
1. the person eating papaya is on the left of the person eating kiwi##1
2. the person eating papaya is on the right of the owner of the goat##1
3. the owner of the chinchilla is between the owner of the goat and the owner of the fish##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |     2      |    3    |
| Food   | apricot | papaya     | kiwi |
| Pet     | goat    | chinchilla | fish    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-6::.
There are 3 different nationalities: dutch, egyptian, indian
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: april, november, august
1. the person who's birthday is in april is between the indian and the dutch##2
2. the dutch is the person who's birthday is in november##1
3. the egyptian is on the right of the dutch##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2      |       3       |
| Nationality   | dutch  | egyptian   | indian        |
| Birthday         | november | april | august |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-7::.
There 3 different types of food: broccoli, carrot, pineapple
3 different games are played: mah-jongg, scrabble, bridge
1. the person eating pineapple is on the right of the person eating broccoli##1
2. the person playing mah-jongg is between the person eating pineapple and the person playing scrabble##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |     3     |
| Food          | carrot  | broccoli  | pineapple |
| Game   | scrabble | mah-jongg | bridge     |

