.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-8::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  dancer, analyst, pilot
There are 3 different nationalities: brazilian, british, mexican
1. the analyst is the mexican##1
2. the british is between the analyst and the pilot##2
3. the analyst is on the right of the dancer##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |    3    |
| Job   | pilot   | dancer  | analyst  |
| Nationality   | brazilian | british | mexican |

