.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-9::.
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: montecristo, ritmeester, oliveros
The people use 3 different means of transport: bus, quad-bike, snowmobile
1. the person driving the bus is on the left of the ritmeester-smoker##1
2. the person driving the bus is between the oliveros-smoker and the person driving the quad-bike##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |       1       |     2      |     3     |
| Cigar       | oliveros | montecristo | ritmeester  |
| Transport   | snowmobile    | bus        | quad-bike |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-10::.
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: tulip, zinnia, lily
The people use 3 different means of transport: car, motorbike, quad-bike
1. the person driving the car is on the right of the person who growslily##1
2. the person who growszinnia is between the person driving the quad-bike and the person who growstulip##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |       1       |   2    |     3     |
| Flower         | lily | zinnia | tulip |
| Transport   | quad-bike     | car    | motorbike |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-11::.
3 different games are played: snooker, monopoly, scrabble
There 3 different types of food: blueberry, kale, zucchini
1. the person eating zucchini is between the person playing monopoly and the person eating blueberry##2
2. the person playing scrabble is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |    2     |     3     |
| Game   | monopoly | snooker      | scrabble      |
| Food       | kale  | zucchini | blueberry |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-12::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: reggae, rock, salsa
The people have 3 different hobbies: board-games, magic-tricks, singing
1. the fan of rock is on the left of the person who's hobby is board-games##1
2. the person who's hobby is singing is between the person who's hobby is board-games and the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##2
3. the fan of reggae is on the left of the fan of rock##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2    |    3    |
| Music-Genre   | reggae | rock   | salsa   |
| Hobby         | magic-tricks | singing | board-games |

