The people prefer 3 different music-genres: country, house, trance
1. the person who's sport is swimming is between the fan of country and the person who's sport is handball##2
2. the fan of trance is on the right of the person who's sport is handball##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |   2    |     3     |
| Sport   | handball | swimming | sailing |
| Music-Genre   | house    | trance | country   |

